
2015-05-25  Samuel Balmand  <Samuel.Balmand@ensg.eu>

	* Version: 0.1
	* Release: first public release

2015-05-29  Samuel Balmand  <Samuel.Balmand@ensg.eu>

	* Version: 0.1-1
	* Release: modification of compiler options

2015-06-12  Samuel Balmand  <Samuel.Balmand@ensg.eu>

	* Version: 0.1-2
	* Release: minor formatting corrections in documentation

2015-06-15  Samuel Balmand  <Samuel.Balmand@ensg.eu>

	* Version: 0.1-3
	* Release: fix cross-platform compilation problems (OS X and Solaris)

2015-10-22  Samuel Balmand  <Samuel.Balmand@ensg.eu>

	* Version: 0.1-4
	* Release: removal of the inclusion of etc/Makeconf for sub-makes, to consider the configuration settings of personnal and site Makevars files instead

2015-11-18  Samuel Balmand  <Samuel.Balmand@ensg.eu>

	* Version: 0.1-5
	* Release: rewriting in C of the functions related to the computation of the matrix of coefficients, memory usage enhancement

2015-11-23  Samuel Balmand  <Samuel.Balmand@ensg.eu>

	* Version: 0.1-6
	* Release: replacing dcopy (BLAS) by memcpy where it produces an unexplained illegal read error when checking the use of memory

2016-04-12  Samuel Balmand  <Samuel.Balmand@ensg.eu>

	* Version: 0.2
	* Release: addition of an implementation of a robust estimator of the precision matrix, addition of a package vignette, modification of the default choice to solve the square-root Lasso problem (set to coordinate descent), functionalities that depend on Mosek or Gurobi tagged as deprecated, modification of the signature of some functions (for instance, two optional parameters were added to DESP_SRL_B() for multithreading and to use shuffled/stochastic coordinate descent, rewriting in C of the function DESP_OLS_B(), other slight improvements

2017-01-31  Samuel Balmand  <Samuel.Balmand@ensg.eu>

	* Version: 0.2-1
	* Release: minor corrections (removal of the -g flag in the makefile scs.mk, removal of references to SUPPORT_OPENMP macro, slight modification of NAMESPACE file)

2017-01-31  Samuel Balmand  <Samuel.Balmand@ensg.eu>

	* Version: 0.2-2
	* Release: minor formatting corrections in DESCRIPTION file
